#
# Save these values securely and update this .env file!

# =============================================================================
# SECURITY CHECKLIST
# =============================================================================
# Before deployment, ensure:
# [ ] All REQUIRED fields above are filled with secure random values
# [ ] SUPER_ADMIN_EMAIL is set to your real email address
# [ ] ALLOWED_ORIGINS matches your actual domain
# [ ] This .env file is not committed to version control
# [ ] Generated passwords are saved in secure password manager
# [ ] Database backups are configured and tested
